Isililo kushona engozini umfundisi nomkakhe NKOSIKHONA CELE KUBHUNTSHE umcimbi wokubungazwa kwabaholi bebandla ngesikhathi umfundisi nomkakhe abebezobungazwa bephelela endleleni engozini enyantisa igazi eyenzeke kuM13, ePinetown, entshonalanga yeTheku, ngoMgqibelo ebusuku. Ligqemeke engeqiwa ntwala ibandla i-Ark Fellowship Centre International (AFCI), ngokudlula emhlabeni kwabaholi balo ababili uMphostoli Bhekokwakhe Ndlovu nomkakhe uPhindile Ndlovu (uMaMngadi). NgeSonto bekumele babungazwe yibandla bebongwa ngendima asebeyiklamile ekuletheni inqubekela phambili kulo selokhu baqala ukulihola ngo-2006. Kuthiwa imoto ebebehamba ngayo iRenault Megane ifahleke yaphela, bona bashonela endaweni yengozi. Kuthiwa ishayiswe yiMercedez yona okusolakala ukuthi ibikade ishayelwa ngowesifazane obedle amponjwana. Lo wesifazane yena kuthiwa usindile. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala, uthe owesifazane oneminyaka engu-35 kutholakale ukuthi ubeshayela ephuzile. Uthe amaphoyisa asePinetown asaphenya. Ngokuthola kweSolezwe, bebekade bephuma ePinetown njengoba bebehambele inkonzo yokuvulwa komuzi welungu lebandla. “Sisadidekile nje sonke. Akukuningi esingakusho,” kusho uNobhala jikelele webandla, uMfundisi Mlindeli Malunga, obezwakala ukuthi kusenzima nakuyena ukwamukela lezi zindaba. Uchaze uNdlovu nomkakhe njengabaholi bekhethelo. Ukuqinisekisile ukuthi bebehlele indumezulu yomcimbi yokubabungaza obuzokuba ngeSonto. Ngemva kokusabalala kwezindaba zokudlula kwabo emhlabeni, sikhulu isililo ezinkundleni zokuxhumana kubazalwane bamahlelo ahlukene. Njengoba ibandla abebelihola belingaphansi kwe-Apostolic Faith Mission, ngesikhathi sokuloba bese beqalile abaholi beFaith Mission bebhonga emswaneni ngaleli fu elimnyama elibagubazele isigubhukane. UMphostoli Collins Dhlomo webandla iCFCI, uthe bafe olwembiza ngokudlula emhlabeni kwalaba. Uthe uNdlovu ubengusihlalo wenhlangano yabefundisi i-Alliance of Pentecoastal and Charismatic Churches of Southern Africa kwisiFunda iTheku. “Lokhu akusikhona ukulimala kwebandla labo nje kuphela kodwa ngukulimala kwebandla likaKristu nje lonke,” kuchaza uDhlomo. Phakathi kwezinye zezinhlelo uNdlovu nowakwakhe abebeziqhuba ngezokunakekelwa kwabadla imbuya ngothi. Baphinda bethula neMove To another Level. Ngalolu hlobo lwenkonzo babehlose ukugqugquzela amalungu ebandla ukuba abe nentshisekelo enkulu yokudlulela kwesinye isigaba sempilo, kunokuthi balibale ukugidagida ndawomye empilweni. Bashiye emhlabeni abantwana babo abane - abafana abathathu nentombazane eyodwa. 